{"tid":1591098,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[香港不合理文化] 痴撚線點解轉工一定要disclose last salary比人壓價?","createTime":"2019-09-24T04:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T07:20:23.000Z","uid":14503,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"26ad00de6ee8cd43b3b8e69623a60dcb3782319b","tid":1591098,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T04:23:35.000Z","msg":"痴撚線點解轉工一定要disclose last salary比人壓價?<br />\n<br />\n其實呢件事好唔合理，份工個職位本身有曬budget幾多錢請人，個個接呢個職位都係做同一樣野，但就死都要跟你上一份工salary加幾多%咁後請，其實好唔公平，即係你上一份工underpay就會一值underpay，外國其實有法例規定新僱主唔可以問員工上一份工salary幾多，係想保障員工唔會被剝削！<br />\n<br />\n香港就係成日咁多呢啲仆街屎劊不成文規定剝削大家！其實係咪應該全民覺醒抵制呢啲唔合理嘅文法？<br />\n<br />\nNew York City ban 左，練問都唔比問，<br />\n香港仲係咁仆街直頭要人比last salary proof?<br />\n唔通呢啲嘢仆街野就唔使反？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.cnbc.com/amp/2017/11/09/how-the-ban-on-asking-whats-your-current-salary-could-affect-you.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Famp%2F2017%2F11%2F09%2Fhow-the-ban-on-asking-whats-your-current-salary-could-affect-you.html&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqIvgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=aa7894e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.cnbc.com/amp/2017/11/09/how-the-ban-on-asking-whats-your-current-salary-could-affect-you.html</a>"},{"pid":"ad9262293af8159fcb2477202626365b8f910346","tid":1591098,"uid":198783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T04:32:04.000Z","msg":"從來都唔會透露<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過有間公司係簽約前叫我比proof, 我同佢講呢個係我私隱，唔會透露，跟住開門走"},{"pid":"dcfaef1f1a74cc08cffdaee9acde2802dc07b7c0","tid":1591098,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:41:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da8a8b3736b716bdfeb056a7ac4fe225ffb93a5b","tid":1591098,"uid":120123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:45:08.000Z","msg":"我覺得reference check根本唔合理。<br />\n如果你同上一份工老細有牙齒印，根本就唔公平。<br />\n呢種制度逼人做狗。<br />\n我有諗過係咪應該禁止。<br />\n但以香港人性格，一定會主動disclose增加議價能力，你話禁止都冇用。"},{"pid":"d51b55d9cfd90512f83670c2ce6846ec3d7351aa","tid":1591098,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:49:00.000Z","msg":"我一路都覺得完全唔合理。<br />\n同埋請人廣告唔出薪金係極唔合理。資訊完全唔對等。<br />\n其實香港勞工界好撚多垃圾文化。"},{"pid":"778766954ae8c131d169ba7b6ba28695372a9bac","tid":1591098,"uid":120123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:48:10.000Z","msg":"其實成件事好撚on9<br />\n僱主的資訊比僱員多好多。<br />\n但台灣定香港試過整個網出來，整合邊個僱主出價幾多，好定唔好，有冇衰野，結果比人告到關站。痴撚線。<br />\n好似最近比人炒左果兩個空姐，因為提出問題比炒，如果你下個僱主係都要追問點解比人炒又reference check又盛，對僱員根本唔公道。"},{"pid":"a4381a1950f92bb85a4f267b668189bed5c1ca05","tid":1591098,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:53:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec46446b989c720d09557bd9761263bd11b58510","tid":1591098,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"點解無人推？<br />\n呢d要反㗎"},{"pid":"7cc6df1f556178d3fbbba8f2253a0da4a833df38","tid":1591098,"uid":155936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"disclosed last salary係咪一定比人壓價?"},{"pid":"74d077ca956d02db6e4b2bfade7f9cb9c7966c57","tid":1591098,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"PUSH"}]}